article:
__NOTOC__ This is a list of Israeli localities, including
Israeli settlements in the West Bank, having standing links to local communities
in other countries. In most cases, the association, especially when formalised
by local government, is known as "town twinning" (though other terms, such as
"partner towns" or "sister cities" are sometimes used instead), and while most
of the places included are towns, the list also comprises villages, cities,
districts, counties, etc. with similar links.
categories: Lists of populated places in Israel
